&lt;p&gt;GitLab is proud to be an equal opportunity workplace and is an affirmative action employer. GitLab’s policies and practices relating to recruitment, employment, career development and advancement, promotion, and retirement are based solely on merit, regardless of race, color, religion, ancestry, sex (including pregnancy, lactation, sexual orientation, gender identity, or gender expression), national origin, age, citizenship, marital status, mental or physical disability, genetic information (including family medical history), discharge status from the military, protected veteran status (which includes disabled veterans, recently separated veterans, active duty wartime or campaign badge veterans, and Armed Forces service medal veterans), or any other basis protected by law. GitLab will not tolerate discrimination or harassment based on any of these characteristics. See also&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/people-policies/inc-usa/#equal-employment-opportunity-policy&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;GitLab’s EEO Policy&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/labor-and-employment-notices/#eeoc-us-equal-employment-opportunity-commission-notices&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;EEO is the Law&lt;/a&gt;. If you have a disability or special need that requires&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/people-policies/inc-usa/#reasonable-accommodation&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;accommodation&lt;/a&gt;, please let us know during the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/hiring/interviewing/#adjustments-to-our-interview-process&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;recruiting process&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Amplitude is the leading AI analytics platform, helping over 4,700 customers—including Atlassian, Burger King, NBCUniversal, Square, and Under Armour—build better products and digital experiences. With powerful AI Agents embedded across our platform, teams can analyze, test, and optimize user experiences faster than ever. Ranked #1 across multiple categories in G2’s Fall 2025 Report, Amplitude is the best-in-class solution for product, data, and marketing teams. Learn more at &lt;a href=&quot;https://cts.businesswire.com/ct/CT?id=smartlink&amp;amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Famplitude.com&amp;amp;esheet=54428090&amp;amp;newsitemid=20260218166598&amp;amp;lan=en-US&amp;amp;anchor=amplitude.com&amp;amp;index=8&amp;amp;md5=6cc9f966d63fa604ba56b7d2bceba4fe&quot;&gt;amplitude.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an organization, we deliver for our customers by living our values. We operate from a place of humility, take ownership of problems and successes, approach challenges with a growth mindset, and put our customers at the center of everything we do.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Amplitude’s Commitment to Diversity Equity &amp;amp; Inclusion (DEI): &lt;/strong&gt;Amplitude believes that diversity enables the creation of better products, improves the ability to solve complex problems, and drives more powerful solutions. We strive to create an environment of inclusion—one focused on psychological safety, empathy, and human connection—that will allow employees of all backgrounds to thrive.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Program Manager, Business Transformation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Amplitude is a leading digital analytics platform that helps companies unlock the power of their products. More than 3,200 customers—including Atlassian, Jersey Mike’s, NBCUniversal, Shopify, and Under Armour—rely on Amplitude to gain self-service visibility into the entire customer journey. Amplitude guides companies every step of the way as they capture data they can trust, uncover clear insights about customer behavior, and take faster action. When teams understand how people are using their products, they can deliver better product experiences that drive growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an organization, we approach challenges with humility, take ownership of our contributions, and embrace a growth mindset that pushes us to constantly improve ourselves, each other, and the value we bring to customers and partners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role &amp;amp; Team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Amplitude is looking for a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Program Manager, Business Transformation&lt;/strong&gt; to drive execution, alignment, and delivery across our highest-priority strategic initiatives. Reporting to the Vice President, Business Transformation, this role operates at the intersection of strategy, execution, and change ensuring that company priorities are planned effectively, delivered with discipline, and adopted across the organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role’s focus will be the programmatic backbone for the Business Transformation portfolio, bringing clarity, structure, accountability, and communication across multiple initiatives that span systems, process, and operating-model change. As well as strategic PM for our large highly complex projects that require a senior level of project management.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an opportunity to play a critical “glue” role at the enterprise level: enabling leaders and teams to move faster and with confidence by providing strong program management, executive visibility, and a steady operating rhythm.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;As a Program Manager &amp;amp; Project Manager, Business Transformation, you will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Program &amp;amp; Portfolio Execution&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the end-to-end delivery of assigned business transformation programs, from planning through execution, launch, and sustained adoption.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate strategic priorities into clear program plans, milestones, dependencies, and success metrics.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help manage weekly top program health tracking progress, risks, decisions, and outcomes across workstreams.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive cross-functional execution without direct authority, ensuring momentum and follow-through.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Delivery Excellence &amp;amp; Continuous Improvement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actively support and evolve Amplitude’s Delivery Excellence practices, including intake, prioritization, planning, tracking, and reporting.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify opportunities to improve delivery predictability, clarity, and execution rigor across the transformation portfolio.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Standardize and maintain program artifacts such as plans, RAID logs, timelines, and status reporting.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Annual &amp;amp; Quarterly Planning&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Business Transformation leadership, Product Owners, and functional teams to support annual and quarterly project and systems planning.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help translate company priorities into an executable portfolio roadmap with clear sequencing and resourcing visibility.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure alignment across initiatives, surfacing tradeoffs and dependencies early.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reporting &amp;amp; Executive Visibility&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own weekly, monthly, and quarterly program reporting for executive audiences.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create clear, concise updates that highlight progress, risks, dependencies, and required decisions.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Synthesize complex information into executive-ready narratives and dashboards.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Program Communications &amp;amp; Enablement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead internal business transformation communications for assigned programs, including program updates, launch communications, and ongoing change messaging.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with Enablement teams to ensure programs are launch-ready and field-ready.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure enablement plans, timelines, and materials are aligned to program milestones and business outcomes.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stakeholder &amp;amp; Executive Partnership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a trusted partner to stakeholders, product owners as well as CE, helping drive alignment and accountability across teams.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate program meetings, capture decisions and action items, and ensure closure.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Anticipate risks and proactively escalate issues with thoughtful options and recommendations.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You’ll be a great addition to the team if you:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6+&amp;nbsp; years of experience in Program Management, Project Management, Business Operations, or Business Transformation roles.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven success managing complex, cross-functional initiatives in a fast-moving, matrixed environment.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong project management fundamentals with exceptional attention to detail and follow-through.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to work directly with executive leadership and senior stakeholders.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience supporting portfolio-level planning, prioritization, and reporting.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong written and verbal communication skills, with the ability to tailor messaging for executives, operators, and the field.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience partnering with Enablement, Operations, or GTM teams to support launches and adoption is a strong plus.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Personality Traits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extreme ownership: Takes full accountability for outcomes, not just activities.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Organized &amp;amp; detail-driven: Brings clarity and rigor to complex, ambiguous work.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Calm &amp;amp; steady: Maintains composure and execution discipline under pressure.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Low-ego, high-impact: Measures success by the effectiveness of the team and the business, not personal visibility.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Service-oriented &amp;amp; collaborative: Operates as a trusted partner across functions and leadership levels.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why This Role Matters&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is foundational to how Amplitude turns strategy into reality.&amp;nbsp; A Business Transformation Project Manager ensures that our most important initiatives are planned well, executed predictably, communicated clearly, and adopted successfully, creating durable business impact rather than one-time delivery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Who We Are&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Company: &lt;/strong&gt;Amplitude is filled with humble, life-long learners who are eager to help one another and the company succeed. Our values of growth mindset, ownership, and humility are core to the way we work: we’re tenacious in the face of challenges, we take the initiative to solve problems that drive our shared success, and we operate from a place of empathy and openness, seeking to understand many points of view.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Product: &lt;/strong&gt;Amplitude is a digital analytics platform—we help companies capture data they can trust, uncover clear insights about customer behavior, and take faster action. This empowers teams to build better product experiences that drive business growth. We’re super proud of what we’ve built and continue to expand: a platform that empowers companies to thrive in the digital era.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We care about the well-being of our team:&lt;/strong&gt; We offer competitive pay and benefits packages that reflect our commitment to the health and well-being of our Ampliteers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Some of our benefit programs include:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
