&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a &lt;strong&gt;passionate, strategic, and customer-obsessed Product Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to drive innovation, shape our roadmap, and lead DBSQL into its next phase of growth.&lt;/p&gt;
