&lt;li&gt;Deep understanding of &lt;strong&gt;SQL, data warehousing, BI, and analytics use cases&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to break down complex problems into &lt;strong&gt;simple, scalable&lt;/strong&gt; solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong sense of &lt;strong&gt;ownership&lt;/strong&gt;—you thrive in ambiguity and love solving hard problems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Experience working with &lt;strong&gt;engineers and designers&lt;/strong&gt; to ship high-impact products.&lt;/li&gt;
