&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Familiarity with data-connector ecosystems&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Experience taking a 0-1 SDK to 10k+ weekly active developers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;History of working in a high-growth company.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;This role represents new headcount added to the team to support continued growth and expansion of capabilities.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
