&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.3;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Click &lt;a href=&quot;https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1CdawUwjo1Q1B7ghZJ_owdmmHB8VtqhBu?usp=sharing&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; to learn more about Fivetran&#39;s Benefits by Region.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.3;&quot;&gt;We’re honored to be &lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://fivetran.com/blog/hvr-acquisition-series-d&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://fivetran.com/blog/hvr-acquisition-series-d&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;valued at over $5.6 billion&lt;/a&gt;, but more importantly, we’re proud of our&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://fivetran.com/culture&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://fivetran.com/culture&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;core values of Get Stuck In, Do the Right Thing, and One Team, One Dream&lt;/a&gt;. Read about us in&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://fivetran-com.s3.amazonaws.com/news/forbes-aug-sept-2022-digital-reprint-10-21-22.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://fivetran-com.s3.amazonaws.com/news/forbes-aug-sept-2022-digital-reprint-10-21-22.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;Forbes&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.3;&quot;&gt;Fivetran brings together high-quality talent across the globe to make data access as easy and reliable as electricity for our customers. We value and recognize that our customers benefit from having innovative teams made of people from many backgrounds, experiences, and identities. Fivetran promotes diversity, equity, inclusion &amp;amp; belonging through attracting, recruiting, developing, and retaining a diverse workforce, not only because it is the right thing to do, but because it helps us build a world-class company to better serve our customers, our people and our communities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.3;&quot;&gt;To learn more about Fivetran’s culture and what it’s like to be part of the team, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xlhtp4dGh8o&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;click here&lt;/a&gt; and enjoy our video.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.3;&quot;&gt;To learn more about our candidate privacy policy, you can &lt;a href=&quot;https://fivetran.com/candidate-privacy&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;read our statement here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.3;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;We are committed to ensuring that all candidates have an equal opportunity to participate in our interview process. If you require accommodations at any stage of the process due to a disability, medical condition, or any other circumstance, please don&#39;t hesitate to submit your request by filling out this &lt;a href=&quot;https://forms.gle/V7k3t4u9j523XkEt6&quot;&gt;form&lt;/a&gt;. We will work with you to provide reasonable accommodations to facilitate your participation and ensure a fair and accessible interview experience. Your request and any information provided will be kept confidential and will not impact your candidacy. We look forward to hearing from you and accommodating your needs to the best of our ability.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;From Fivetran’s founding until now, our mission has remained the same: to make access to data as simple and reliable as electricity. With Fivetran, customer data arrives in their warehouses, canonical and ready to query, with no engineering or maintenance required. We’re proud that more organizations continue to leverage our technology every day to become truly data-driven.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;As a Senior Product Manager, Data Processing Engine, you will manage the central, highly leveraged data product at Fivetran that powers millions of data syncs each day, across hundreds of thousands of unique data connections, for over ten thousand Fivetran customers. Fivetran has long been on a mission to make access to data as simple and easy to use as electricity, and our Data Processing Engine is the core product that does that.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;This role has significant exposure to customers, whose unique data requirements drive the majority of the roadmap. This role also has aspects that are similar to a traditional “platform PM” role, in that you will work closely with other PMs and engineering teams to ensure that our system supports their use cases. Your most important role will be helping to steer and rationalize these requests to achieve a balance between ease of use and powerful expressiveness.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;You’ll collaborate closely with the rest of the product management team, and with a highly engaged leadership team. If you can chart a clear course, and build alignment by bringing your stakeholders along, the potential for highly visible impact is significant!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;This is a full-time, hybrid position that is based out of our Oakland, CA office.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Deeply understand the data problems our customers are trying to solve with Fivetran from multiple aspects: schema evolution, data semantics, transformation compatibility, performance, security, and reliability&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Use a variety of analytical skills to study these problems, including ad-hoc data analyses from relational &amp;amp; telemetry data, customer surveys and interviews, and first-principles reasoning&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Collaborate with engineering and design to clearly specify solutions that artfully solve the problems your customers are facing in alignment with our product principles&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Build and manage the data processing roadmap; set quarterly goals and track deliverables and results&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Evangelize the success of your initiatives internally and, in collaboration with product marketing, externally&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Heavily collaborate with colleagues across product management&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Hold yourself accountable with release/adoption performance metrics, and report on this quarterly in the spirit of continuous improvement&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skills We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Excellent data analytics capabilities using modern data tools — you’re good with spreadsheets and SQL, but can also break out something like Pandas, NumPy, etc. when it’s needed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Good product design taste in data software — a strong intuition for what makes a data product tick, and how to extend it while preserving a premium product experience.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Recent experience managing data software products, including shipping measurable impact&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;You’ve run a customer facing migration project and can talk at length about what you learned from that experience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;A technical foundation — you know about software interfaces and type systems, you can reason about the merits of row-oriented and column-oriented data storage, and you can draw a roughly accurate architecture diagram for the last system you worked on. You may not write the software that you ship, but you make sure to understand it.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
