&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;From Fivetran’s founding until now, our mission has remained the same: to make access to data as simple and reliable as electricity. With Fivetran, customer data arrives in their warehouses, canonical and ready to query, with no engineering or maintenance required. We’re proud that more organizations continue to leverage our technology every day to become truly data-driven.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;We’re looking for an experienced Product Manager to own Monitoring and Observability—a critical pillar of our Enterprise Platform group. In this role, you will help our largest and most sophisticated customers easily understand how their data pipelines are performing. You&#39;ll focus on delivering a world-class observability experience, ensuring that Fivetran remains easy to use even as our capabilities expand in scale and complexity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;We’re looking for someone who can bring AI-native thinking to how our platform evolves—whether it’s in accelerating development with intelligent defaults, enabling automated observability, or expanding how customers build with Fivetran programmatically.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;This is a high-impact, high-visibility role, perfect for product leaders who thrive on technical challenges, tight feedback loops, and opportunities to shape long-term platform strategy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;This is a full-time, hybrid position based out of our Oakland, CA or Denver, CO office. Our hybrid work model offers a blend of remote flexibility and in-person collaboration, including two days in the office each week to connect and build as a team.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Own and evolve the Monitoring &amp;amp; Observability product area: logging, alerting, sync status, latency monitoring, event standardization, and external integrations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Develop a strategic roadmap that improves transparency into Fivetran connection behavior, with a focus on supporting Enterprise-grade monitoring requirements.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Partner closely with engineering and design to deliver intuitive experiences for customers to monitor, debug, and optimize their data syncs—and integrate seamlessly with their existing observability stack.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Prioritize product investments based on revenue-weighted feature usage, customer feedback, support ticket trends, and roadmap alignment with adjacent platform teams.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Serve as the subject matter expert for observability across Fivetran and champion platform consistency in user experience and technical implementation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Drive cross-functional alignment and go-to-market readiness for major product launches.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Stay on the pulse of trends in developer platforms, data infrastructure, and enterprise tooling—with an eye toward AI-first opportunities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skills We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Product management experience in B2B SaaS or platform products.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Demonstrated success leading technical products with high customer expectations for reliability and observability.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Strong technical fluency—comfortable working with logs, events, monitoring pipelines, and API-based integrations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Proven collaboration skills across Engineering, Design, Support, and GTM.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Data-informed mindset with experience using both qualitative and quantitative inputs to drive prioritization.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Ability to execute cross-functionally in a high-growth, fast-paced environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus Skills&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
