&lt;li&gt;Analytical skills with proficiency in Excel/Sheets and basic data tools (e.g. Looker, Tableau, or Salesforce reporting).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent attention to detail and follow-through.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
