&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep experience creating and growing products leveraging video data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facility with development and deployment of AI/ML models, including training and evaluation pipelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding or experience with foundation models, model quantization and distillation.&lt;/li&gt;
