&lt;li&gt;Text2SQL business intelligence applications to make analysts more efficient and embed a culture of data-driven decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an experienced product manager to join our team and play a pivotal role in building AI solutions with and for our customers. The ideal candidate will have a strong understanding of software engineering principles and practices and deep experience with ML/AI application development. You will be responsible for owning large AI projects for one or many customers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
