&lt;p&gt;Scale AI is a 2-sided marketplace. On the demand side we have customers that need labeled data to train their AI models or AI applications. On the supply side we have millions of contributors distributed worldwide.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The biggest business problem we currently face is: identifying the right contributors from across the globe to complete tasks on a specific project. Identifying the right users enables us to deliver higher quality data to our customers sooner, with less waste.&lt;/p&gt;
