&lt;p&gt;This role spans two complementary but distinct areas of ownership:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. AI‑Led Discovery &amp;amp; Innovation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Owning the vision and execution for AI‑driven discovery experiences that help retailers move from inspiration to buyable assortments, leveraging things like text and image generation and multi-turn chat capabilities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Search Experience&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Owning the UX for Faire’s search experiences, ensuring retailers can quickly and confidently find what they’re looking for. This includes zero state, suggestions, filters, result presentation, and overall usability—partnering closely with Search Algorithm teams where query understanding, retrieval or ranking changes are required.&lt;/p&gt;
