&lt;p&gt;Compensation may be adjusted depending on work location.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-root=&quot;1&quot;&gt;For Washington D.C. based hires: Estimated annual salary of $158,000-$218,000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
